cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL

This paper deals with deep learning models and their performance on vision tasks, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on improving the diversity of ensembles for better generalization and uncertainty estimation, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) or computer vision (cs.CV).
